Peter,

I wanted to reach out and thank you for all of your support. Whether you have stepped up with a generous donation, attended one of our town halls, told your friends about our campaign, or took the time to sign a petition, I am grateful to have you on my team.

This race is going to be a tough race. It&rsquo;s never easy to go up against an incumbent, and we both know that Democrats are pouring resources into this race to try and protect Sorensen. But we also know the people of our district are ready for a change. We are tired and fed up with politicians like Sorensen leaving hardworking families behind and prioritizing politics over people.

The bottom line: There is too much on the line for us to sit back and do nothing. We&rsquo;ve got to keep fighting every day to flip this seat and restore law and order in Washington.

That&rsquo;s why every dollar makes such a critical impact in this race, and it&rsquo;s why I&rsquo;m so grateful to have people like you on my team.

Thank you,

Judge Joe McGraw

